!!【柯林斯英汉双解大词典】

:<div>

electrical /ɪˈlɛktrɪkəl/

1. ADJ Electrical goods, equipment, or appliances work by means of electricity. 电力的 

例： ...shipments of electrical equipment. …电器设备的运输。 

2. electrically ADV 电力地 [ADV -ed] 

例： ...electrically powered vehicles. …电动车。 

3. ADJ Electrical systems or parts supply or use electricity. 电的 

例： ...lighting and other electrical systems on the new runway. …新跑道上的照明和其他电力系统。 

4. ADJ Electrical energy is energy in the form of electricity. 电的 

例： ...brief pulses of electrical energy. …短暂的电能脉冲。 

5. electrically ADV 电地 

例： ...electrically charged particles. …带电的粒子。 

6. ADJ Electrical industries, engineers, or workers are involved in the production and supply of electricity or electrical products. 与电有关的 [ADJ n] 

例： ...company representatives from the electrical industry. …来自电力行业的公司代表。

</div>

